ppily have my security"],[2886,3015,"drag you out of here."],[3069,3157,"Ms. Sterling,"],[3224,3520,"we've known Cassius for over six years,"],[3520,3720,"and he's been the same pathetic,"],[3749,3995,"desperate nobody the entire time!"],[3995,4095,"You have to believe-"],[4095,4158,"Enough!"],[4216,4483,"I will not tolerate baseless rumors."],[4533,4650,"Do you want to hear the truth?"],[4725,4846,"With a single phone call,"],[4846,5013,"Cassius was able to solve a crisis"],[5013,5205,"that even I was powerless to solve."],[5292,5426,"You think any of you"],[5480,5609,"have the right to question him?"],[5726,5860,"Or slander him?"],[5955,6068,"You know, Isabella,"],[6131,6218,"I should thank you."],[6277,6481,"If it wasn't for your ignorance,"],[6552,6690,"I wouldn't have been lucky enough"],[6748,6923,"to meet this incredible husband"],[6973,7140,"and wonderful father to my child."]],"22":[[12,216,"Okay, who in the hell"],[216,354,"is this Cassius guy?"],[354,467,"And why is Ms. Sterling"],[467,579,"treating him like royalty?"],[625,684,"Isabella,"],[804,905,"I took parole just so"],[905,996,"I could propose to you"],[996,1105,"before Thanksgiving,"],[1197,1301,"and make you the happiest"],[1301,1384,"woman in the world."],[1514,1643,"And all I got in return"],[1730,1856,"was humiliation,"],[1856,1922,"betrayal,"],[1931,2027,"and slander."],[2427,2531,"But now, that's in the past."],[2836,2898,"We're over."],[3244,3361,"Cassius,"],[3386,3511,"after all that bluffing,"],[3511,3632,"you're still just a criminal."],[3632,3716,"Oh, trust me."],[3778,4004,"When you finally learn who I really am,"],[4070,4200,"all you'll feel is regret."],[4258,4354,"Ms. Sterling said"],[4354,4504,"he solved all her problems."],[4554,4725,"Does she mean Cassius is the one"],[4725,4909,"who crushed all those rumors"],[4909,5163,"about Ms. Sterling and Mirror Media?"]],"23":[[183,387,"Okay, rein it in, boys."],[421,638,"Cassius has been stuck in the slammer"],[638,759,"for the past six years."],[759,892,"You really think that"],[892,1055,"he solved an issue"],[1055,1188,"that the Queen of News"],[1188,1284,"couldn't fix herself?"],[1380,1501,"Ms. Sterling."],[1572,1768,"I know Cassius better than anyone."],[1818,1997,"He's just here for your money."],[1997,2068,"Isabella,"],[2147,2277,"what makes you so sure"],[2277,2444,"you can read people better than I can?"],[2523,2665,"If you weren't so pathetic,"],[2669,2794,"I might be insulted."],[2940,3107,"Meeting this man and marrying him"],[3194,3274,"has been the best thing"],[3274,3382,"that's ever happened to me."],[3482,3520,"Yeah!"],[3536,3678,"My daddy's super cool!"],[3920,4029,"Cassius,"],[4095,4346,"I cannot fathom what type of voodoo"],[4346,4571,"you did to wrap Ms. Sterling"],[4571,4679,"around your finger."],[4679,4909,"But I swear to God,"],[4921,5155,"I will not let some broke chump"],[5155,5363,"like you keep me from landing this job!"],[5363,5434,"Oh, really?"],[5547,5668,"Because my husband brought up"],[5668,5834,"a really good point earlier."],[5893,5968,"Isabella,"],[6018,6156,"in light of your shameful"],[6156,6268,"behavior tonight,"],[6297,6456,"I'd like to officially notify you that"],[6456,6656,"your contract with Mirror Media"],[6690,6819,"has officially been terminated."],[6898,7036,"Congratulations,"],[7057,7157,"you're fired."]],"24":[[4,50,"What?"],[187,250,"Why?"],[337,487,"No, no, no. Ms,"],[487,625,"Ms. Sterling, you can't."],[729,834,"You, you can't,"],[834,1126,"you can't just obliterate my career"],[1126,1351,"because of some criminal!"],[1351,1668,"I'm, I'm a Pulitzer nominee!"],[1718,1764,"I..."],[1843,1922,"Well, yeah, yeah."],[1964,2085,"With Isabella on board,"],[2122,2243,"Mirror Media was headed"],[2243,2339,"straight to the top."],[2339,2469,"You can't just can her"],[2469,2665,"because of this lying sack of trash."],[2665,2731,"Oh, really?"],[2748,2840,"Who's lying here?"],[2911,3040,"You've been spreading lies about"],[3040,3215,"my loyal, loving husband,"],[3215,3382,"and father to my daughter all night."],[3457,3582,"And Mirror Media takes slander"],[3582,3716,"very seriously."],[3791,3849,"Brooke?"],[4074,4200,"Anyone who's disrespected"],[4200,4279,"my husband?"],[4337,4433,"Throw them out."],[4483,4625,"And cancel all the deals that"],[4625,4758,"Mirror Media has with them."],[4783,4925,"It's time they learn the cost of"],[4925,5130,"talking ill about my husband."],[5180,5255,"Yes, ma'am."],[5338,5426,"You heard her."],[5451,5551,"Throw them out!"],[5559,5613,"Yes, ma'am."],[5613,5714,"No, no, no, no."],[5876,5935,"It's over."],[6064,6122,"It's over."],[6260,6302,"No."],[6335,6406,"No!"],[6456,6531,"No!"],[6610,6715,"No!"],[6806,6881,"No!"],[6915,6990,"It's over."],[7011,7052,"No."]],"25":[[66,158,"No!"],[471,533,"Go!"],[550,675,"Cassius, please."],[675,834,"You can't let her do this to me."],[859,1055,"I, I didn't mean it, please."],[1055,1230,"You have to save me."],[1297,1384,"I told you,"],[1384,1505,"you would be filled with regret."],[1626,1760,"Now there's nothing for you to do"],[1760,1847,"except drown in there."],[1914,2002,"Hold it!"],[2127,2198,"I've been sent by"],[2198,2339,"the Enros Group secretary"],[2339,2456,"Warren Franco"],[2456,2606,"to give a special delivery"],[2606,2806,"for a Isabella Davis."],[2877,2998,"I'm Isabella Davis!"],[3503,3682,"Congratulations, Ms. Davis."],[3699,3924,"You've been granted exclusive access"],[3937,4070,"to an interview with Mr. S"],[4070,4187,"from the Enros Group."],[4216,4283,"Mr. Franco will"],[4283,4421,"be in touch very shortly"],[4421,4517,"to coordinate the interview."],[4846,4896,"Hello?"],[4934,5013,"Mr. Warren?"],[5055,5234,"Yes, thank you so much"],[5234,5326,"for this opportunity!"],[5326,5442,"I won't waste it!"],[5459,5597,"Oh shoot."],[5659,5830,"I forgot to cancel this."],[5847,6010,"Mr. S himself personally"],[6010,6164,"requested you to interview him."],[6164,6289,"He'd also like to inform you"],[6289,6418,"that he's been your benefactor"],[6418,6573,"for the past six years."],[6602,6765,"Mr. S plans to make an"],[6765,6848,"appearance at the gala"],[6848,6944,"later this evening."],[6990,7090,"Enjoy your big night."]],"26":[[129,183,"Pamela!"],[183,350,"Do you know what this means?"],[362,600,"An exclusive interview with Mr. S,"],[600,880,"that's the biggest get in journalism!"],[888,1063,"And he's been helping my career"],[1063,1188,"the entire time!"],[1188,1272,"I know."],[1388,1501,"Mr. S?"],[1522,1622,"The mystery man"],[1622,1814,"who never shows his face in public?"],[1814,1951,"The one who has the president"],[1951,2085,"at his beck and call?"],[2152,2369,"The richest man in the world?"],[2519,2610,"That's right."],[2694,2836,"Ms. Sterling,"],[2861,2982,"drop Cassius,"],[2982,3115,"raise my original offer to"],[3115,3269,"two hundred million,"],[3269,3453,"and I might consider"],[3453,3582,"rejoining Mirror Media."],[3616,3716,"We both know"],[3716,3853,"that if your company drops"],[3853,4029,"this exclusive on Mr. S,"],[4029,4137,"Mirror Media won’t just"],[4137,4270,"dominate the country,"],[4304,4550,"it'll dominate the goddamn world."],[4713,4783,"Ms. Sterling,"],[4783,4946,"an exclusive with Mr. S"],[4946,5055,"would be huge."],[5063,5159,"We've been trying to get him"],[5159,5280,"to talk to us for years."],[5751,5793,"No."],[6177,6373,"Mirror Media has zero interest"],[6373,6577,"in partnering with this self-serving,"],[6577,6752,"arrogant fool such as yourself."],[6785,6869,"Even if that means"],[6869,7052,"losing the exclusive with Mr. S,"],[7052,7186,"I simply can't overlook"],[7186,7357,"the disrespect you have"],[7357,7494,"shown my husband this evening."],[7824,7903,"Figures."],[7928,8070,"You know, Freya Sterling,"],[8070,8229,"I thought you were different."],[8229,8404,"Ruthless, cut-throat."],[8433,8612,"Turns out you're just"],[8612,8808,"a soft-minded fool."],[8867,9017,"Oh, that's fine by me."],[9017,9225,"I mean, once I drop this exclusive,"],[9250,9405,"I'll be the Queen of News."],[9405,9492,"So have fun"],[9492,9597,"watching from the sidelines"],[9597,9709,"while I steal your throne."],[9914,10030,"I can't believe Freya would"],[10030,10226,"make such a big sacrifice just for me."],[10339,10477,"I need to make her choice worth it."],[10606,10664,"Hey."],[10777,10848,"Don't worry."],[10977,11111,"Because one phone call from me,"],[11156,11240,"and the Enros Group"],[11240,11382,"will pull that exclusive interview"],[11382,11473,"right out of your hands."]],"27":[[4,83,"And the Enros Group"],[83,212,"will pull that exclusive interview"],[212,362,"right out of your hands."],[704,809,"Oh my gosh,"],[829,992,"what did you just say, Cassius?"],[1051,1113,"No, like really."],[1113,1230,"Can you repeat it again?"],[1230,1434,"Because I could use another laugh."],[1526,1634,"He's so confident."],[1668,1776,"Is Cassius some kind of"],[1776,1901,"higher-up at Enros Group?"],[1914,2010,"That's why no one can dig up"],[2010,2085,"his background?"],[2127,2189,"But still,"],[2243,2323,"who the hell is he?"],[2448,2644,"Oh my god, did you guys hear him?"],[2669,2823,"Cassius is gonna take away"],[2823,2965,"Isabella's exclusive."],[3015,3178,"Do you think that Mr. S cares"],[3178,3328,"at all what you think?"],[3357,3461,"What are you, some big shot?"],[3503,3566,"Bingo."],[3699,3912,"Cassius, you've been locked up"],[3912,4045,"for the past six years,"],[4045,4220,"so let me get you up to date."],[4220,4446,"The Enros Group is the biggest"],[4446,4633,"media powerhouse on the planet."],[4637,4779,"I mean, even the president"],[4779,4925,"wouldn't be here without them today."],[4925,5121,"So, little word of advice."],[5121,5242,"I'd make yourself scarce"],[5242,5401,"before Mr. S gets here."],[5401,5572,"Once he hears the bullshit"],[5572,5668,"you've been spewing,"],[5668,5839,"you'll be a dead man walking."],[5864,5947,"Oh, is that so?"],[6093,6181,"Cassius."],[6252,6368,"I know there's more to you"],[6368,6452,"than meets the eye,"],[6452,6698,"but this is Mr. S we're talking about."],[6710,6819,"She's not worth it."],[6819,6948,"Don't worry, Mommy,"],[6981,7102,"Daddy is more amazing than"],[7102,7211,"anyone in the world."],[7290,7357,"Hey."],[7507,7590,"Trust me."]],"28":[[321,354,"Warren,"],[442,504,"remember those"],[504,663,"exclusive interview rights"],[663,846,"you gave to Isabella Davis?"],[934,1021,"Retract them now."],[1180,1234,"Cute."],[1234,1434,"Real cute, Cassius."],[1447,1497,"What, you think"],[1497,1634,"Secretary Warren is just gonna"],[1659,1764,"do what you say"],[1764,1881,"just because you told him to?"],[1981,2035,"Three."],[2097,2202,"Just quit embarrassing"],[2202,2348,"yourself and fuck off."],[2394,2444,"Two."],[2494,2677,"Cassius, stop turning this place"],[2677,2857,"into a circus, you clown."],[2923,2965,"One."],[3453,3653,"That must be Mr. S arriving."],[3703,3741,"Oh."],[3912,4037,"Everybody listen to this."],[4091,4250,"Hello, Ms. Isabella Davis."],[4283,4375,"I regret to inform you"],[4375,4496,"that as per direct orders"],[4496,4583,"from the highest level of"],[4583,4679,"the Enros Group,"],[4688,4850,"your exclusive interview rights"],[4850,5063,"with Mr. S are hereby revoked."],[5117,5167,"What?"],[5342,5492,"What, you can't do that."],[5555,5584,"What?"],[5584,5739,"No, no, Mr. Warren,"],[5759,5914,"well, you can't, they can't do that."],[5968,6085,"So tell me, Isabella,"],[6256,6348,"who's the clown now?"]],"29":[[20,145,"They, they can't do this."],[145,379,"They can't just take away my interview."],[421,475,"Why they..."],[567,696,"Cassius,"],[734,934,"who the hell are you?"],[955,1051,"How do you even know"],[1051,1226,"the Enros Secretary Group?"],[1263,1426,"Well, who I am doesn't matter."],[1451,1555,"What does matter is"],[1555,1680,"you finally realizing"],[1680,1847,"just how clueless you've been."],[2072,2210,"Was I wrong about Cassius"],[2210,2302,"this whole time?"],[2344,2560,"What if he's really some low-key,"],[2560,2694,"behind-the-scenes big shot?"],[2715,2877,"God, was dumping him actually"],[2877,3023,"some type of career suicide?"],[3086,3349,"Hey, don't freak out, sis."],[3365,3607,"Sure, so Cassius knows a guy"],[3607,3699,"who knows a guy,"],[3699,3837,"but don't you forget,"],[3883,3970,"Mr. S,"],[3970,4279,"handpicked you for that exclusive."],[4279,4383,"Plus, he was backing you"],[4383,4537,"for years before this."],[4579,4779,"Just turn up the charm"],[4779,4879,"when he gets here"],[4879,5000,"and you'll snatch back"],[5000,5234,"those exclusive rights no problem."],[5234,5288,"Yeah."],[5326,5417,"Yeah, you're right."],[5459,5530,"Mr. S has been"],[5530,5638,"backing me for years."],[5638,5843,"He clearly believes in my talent."],[5843,5910,"There's no way"],[5910,6043,"he would take away my interview."],[6118,6285,"Lying to yourself now, Isabella?"],[6406,6493,"Not good journalism."],[6577,6856,"Oh, shut the fuck up, Cassius."],[6869,7032,"When Mr. S walks in,"],[7032,7240,"that exclusive will be back in my hands."],[7240,7503,"And I'll sell it to a real media giant"],[7503,7665,"and take over the entire"],[7682,7791,"fucking industry"],[7791,8112,"while you and Mirror Media rot."],[8249,8304,"Oh, really?"],[8420,8558,"And what if I told you."],[8717,8829,"I'm Mr. S."]],"30":[[29,137,"I'm Mr. S."],[596,804,"Oh my god, Cassius!"],[825,1005,"Have you lost your mind?"],[1034,1230,"Oh, Ms. Sterling, do you really"],[1230,1388,"want to give up this exclusive"],[1409,1680,"for some wacko in fantasy world?"],[1726,1885,"My question exactly."],[3290,3453,"Freya, I cannot believe"],[3453,3528,"that you gave up"],[3528,3716,"an exclusive with Mr. S."],[3716,3791,"You might as well have given"],[3791,3899,"over Mirror Media to me."],[3970,4083,"You seriously"],[4083,4204,"married this fucking loser?"],[4204,4437,"Have you forgotten that I'm your fiancé?"],[4529,4654,"Preston, I wouldn't marry you"],[4654,4813,"if you were the last man on earth."]],"31":[[12,45,"Wait."],[104,250,"Freya was gonna marry Preston,"],[266,412,"the Norton family heir?"],[421,667,"They've got hundreds of billions."],[667,842,"Even if Cassius has connections,"],[867,984,"Freya's totally nuts to give up"],[984,1059,"on the Norton money."],[1096,1155,"For real."],[1222,1313,"Unless,"],[1326,1472,"Cassius is somehow"],[1472,1634,"an even bigger deal than Preston?"],[1722,1789,"Please."],[1814,1989,"Preston runs all of the major"],[1989,2181,"news companies in the state."],[2202,2314,"Sure, Cassius might have"],[2314,2398,"a couple connections,"],[2398,2485,"but he's nothing"],[2485,2623,"compared to the Norton heir."],[2640,2740,"Freya, I'm sure you recognize"],[2740,2802,"my friends here."],[2802,2965,"The CEOs of three biggest"],[2965,3086,"media giants."],[3136,3244,"They have the power"],[3244,3390,"to destroy your empire with"],[3390,3516,"the flick of a wrist."],[3516,3628,"So I will give you"],[3670,3803,"one last chance."],[3862,4033,"Divorce this convicted felon,"],[4033,4116,"marry me,"],[4145,4354,"or I will wipe Mirror Media"],[4354,4525,"off the face of the map."],[4617,4738,"Fuck you, Preston!"],[4892,4938,"Hey, dickwad."],[4938,5105,"This is the part where you turn tail"],[5105,5209,"and get the fuck out of here"],[5209,5405,"before I put you back in your jail cell"],[5405,5476,"where you belong."],[5547,5705,"You're a dead man, Preston Norton."],[5926,6018,"You were dead the second"],[6018,6143,"you threatened my wife."],[6306,6456,"Now all that's left for you to do"],[6560,6685,"is watch your entire family"],[6685,6806,"crumble to pieces."]],"32":[[33,150,"Is watch your entire family"],[150,258,"crumble to pieces."],[433,517,"Cassius, is it?"],[529,650,"See, what all I see"],[650,759,"here is gutter trash"],[763,875,"who's trying to make ends meet."],[875,955,"Because you don't even know"],[955,1146,"what the Norton family is capable of."],[1192,1259,"But don't worry,"],[1326,1422,"you're gonna learn"],[1488,1568,"the hard way."],[1918,1951,"Preston,"],[1951,2052,"what the hell are you doing?"],[2089,2198,"Freya, I can't believe you're still"],[2198,2268,"sticking up for this guy."],[2268,2402,"You only met him today."],[2427,2527,"I have been by your side"],[2527,2627,"since we were kids."],[2627,2761,"Not to mention he publicly"],[2761,2907,"insulted the Norton name."],[2907,3098,"It's only right that I punish him."],[3144,3257,"Don't worry about that."],[3303,3415,"You go be a good girl"],[3415,3516,"and start prepping our"],[3516,3636,"engagement ceremony, huh?"],[3657,3757,"Back off!"],[3812,3962,"No one bullies my mommy."],[4049,4279,"Preston, if you put a hand on Cassius,"],[4291,4491,"I will see to it that you are finished."],[4583,4650,"Do you hear that?"],[4650,4871,"I think she's insulting me."],[4900,5009,"Freya, you may want to think"],[5009,5067,"this over."],[5109,5188,"When you cross Preston,"],[5188,5363,"you make enemies of us as well."],[5405,5476,"You're damn right!"],[5547,5676,"And from this moment forward,"],[5722,5839,"my company doesn't do"],[5839,6060,"any business with Mirror Media."],[6110,6181,"Same here."],[6252,6489,"Freya, consider all ties to my company"],[6506,6706,"null and void from here forward."]],"33":[[12,212,"The top three media giants"],[212,367,"just cut ties with Mirror Media?"],[404,521,"Ms. Sterling's toast."],[579,734,"See that, Cassius?"],[759,871,"Real power is when you hold"],[871,1046,"all the cards in your own hands."],[1067,1167,"You've just been doing"],[1167,1313,"other people's dirty work."],[1313,1418,"That's not power,"],[1468,1639,"that's being a goddamn lapdog."],[1780,1972,"You must be Isabella Davis,"],[1972,2097,"the new hotshot journalist"],[2097,2285,"who's gotten the attention of Mr. S."],[2302,2385,"You know, I'm always looking for"],[2385,2464,"a new talent,"],[2594,2794,"especially one so easy on the eyes."],[2794,2927,"Thank you, Mr. Norton."],[2957,3098,"I'd love working with you."],[3294,3415,"Mr. Norton."],[3465,3586,"My firm's got real potential."],[3591,3657,"If you're interested,"],[3657,3716,"we can sit down and talk."],[3716,3824,"Mr. Norton, my firm!"],[3862,3995,"Mr. Norton, you need to come to us."],[3999,4066,"Mr. Norton."],[4079,4162,"Mr. Norton."],[4162,4241,"You see, Freya?"],[4283,4375,"This is what happens"],[4375,4500,"when people go against me."],[4500,4650,"I take everything that they've built"],[4692,4808,"and I turn it into dust,"],[4854,4929,"just like that."],[4984,5071,"Are you sure you still want to"],[5071,5263,"side with this pathetic con-man?"],[5334,5463,"I've made my choice,"],[5534,5651,"and it's Cassius."],[5801,5922,"I'm sticking with him."],[5960,6035,"Ride or die."],[6660,6815,"Now that is the woman I married."],[6915,7090,"I'm lucky to be your man, Freya."],[7136,7194,"And you know what?"],[7265,7369,"I'm not gonna let anything"],[7369,7482,"happen to Mirror Media."],[7482,7557,"In fact,"],[7636,7786,"I'm gonna take it straight to the top."]],"34":[[8,154,"I'm gonna take it straight to the top."],[250,304,"Cassius,"],[304,550,"have you finally lost your mind?"],[592,742,"Why don't you do yourself a favor"],[742,855,"and go look in a mirror"],[855,1030,"at the fraud that you are?"],[1051,1267,"It is called Mirror Media, after all."],[1280,1526,"Do you even hear yourself, Cassius?"],[1564,1676,"Ms. Sterling gave up"],[1676,1830,"an exclusive interview"],[1830,2018,"with Mirror Media for you."],[2077,2152,"And what?"],[2160,2335,"You're just gonna stand here and"],[2335,2469,"run your mouth while Mirror Media's"],[2469,2644,"on the brink of collapse?"],[2702,2936,"He's a lost cause, Ms. Sterling."],[2973,3048,"Cut him loose."],[3098,3219,"Maybe you can save your company."],[3349,3591,"Mommy, you've got to trust Daddy!"],[3632,3774,"I believe in you, Daddy."],[3812,3895,"You can do it."],[4049,4254,"This poor little girl doesn't know shit."],[4308,4437,"Your Mommy and your Daddy"],[4437,4546,"are dunzo, kid."],[4546,4688,"She barely got Mirror Media"],[4688,4792,"into the top ten."],[4829,5017,"And she's still miles behind us."],[5034,5171,"And now that we've joined forces,"],[5196,5405,"her little media enterprise?"],[5442,5555,"Dead in the water."],[5601,5747,"If that clown really thinks"],[5747,5805,"they're going to put"],[5805,5972,"Mirror Media above us?"],[6043,6239,"That's next-level delusion."],[6314,6431,"And what if I told you"],[6527,6669,"that I could land Mirror Media"],[6669,6865,"an interview with Mr. S, and,"],[7107,7219,"an exclusive long-term"],[7219,7349,"partnership with Enros Group."]],"35":[[33,154,"An exclusive long-term"],[154,275,"partnership with Enros Group."],[333,454,"If that happens,"],[454,608,"Mirror Media really would shoot to"],[608,671,"number one."],[713,821,"But that's impossible."],[855,959,"Mirror Media's nothing,"],[1013,1197,"barely a blip on Enros Group's radar."],[1238,1418,"Let alone the legendary Mr. S."],[1822,1931,"Wow!"],[1972,2102,"It looks like even losers"],[2102,2264,"who've been in prison for six years"],[2264,2448,"have heard of the brilliant Mr. S"],[2448,2556,"and his Enros Group."],[2565,2644,"But you still don't know"],[2644,2752,"what you're talking about."],[2777,2923,"You see, he is the man"],[2969,3044,"behind the president."],[3044,3199,"The undisputed king of finance."],[3199,3365,"How could someone like you"],[3386,3678,"possibly have a deal locked in with him?"],[3753,3903,"For Mirror fucking Media?"],[3945,4041,"What a joke."],[4041,4237,"Enros Group is the crown jewel"],[4237,4346,"in global finance."],[4346,4483,"We can't even get our foot in the door."],[4491,4592,"Mirror Media?"],[4642,4713,"Forget about it."],[4771,4913,"Shit, and the Norton family had to"],[4913,5071,"pull every string we had just to"],[5113,5259,"get a seat at the negotiation table"],[5259,5363,"with Enros Group."],[5434,5580,"I still didn't get a glimpse of"],[5580,5689,"Mr. S's face."],[5801,5830,"You know what?"],[5830,5872,"No!"],[5943,6056,"How does a nobody like you"],[6056,6185,"fresh out of prison possibly"],[618