n!"],[6560,6823,"I'm not a bastard, I have a daddy."],[6881,6990,"You're a bastard!"]],"38":[[212,296,"Oh, buddy."],[725,813,"Ignoring my warnings"],[813,888,"is one thing."],[946,1063,"But trying to hit a kid?"],[1217,1326,"It's time for the Norton family"],[1326,1451,"to be wiped off the map."],[1572,1668,"You just hit me."],[1697,1868,"You just fucking hit me."],[1931,1997,"Security!"],[2043,2110,"Get him!"],[2139,2273,"And make him fucking bleed."],[2327,2464,"Enros Group Secretary"],[2464,2640,"Warren Franco has arrived."],[3370,3428,"Good evening."],[3503,3603,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[3641,3732,"I'd like to announce,"],[3732,3862,"effective immediately,"],[3891,4104,"the Enros Group entering into"],[4104,4320,"an exclusive partnership"],[4375,4491,"with Mirror Media."],[4896,4975,"Cassius."],[5092,5159,"Who are you?"]],"39":[[16,104,"Who are you?"],[583,775,"Daddy, you're the coolest."],[1159,1217,"I'm sorry."],[1217,1322,"What the hell is happening,"],[1355,1413,"right now?"],[1413,1593,"Why on earth would Enros Group"],[1622,1785,"partner with Mirror Media?"],[1814,1968,"Mr. Norton, if I'm not mistaken,"],[1968,2102,"didn't you previously submit"],[2102,2235,"a Mirror Media partnership"],[2235,2377,"proposal with Enros Group"],[2377,2506,"on behalf of your family?"],[2535,2673,"Could it be that this is all"],[2715,2786,"your doing?"],[2786,2877,"That's right, thank you."],[2877,3148,"Cassius, you sneaky bastard."],[3203,3349,"You almost got away with it, too."],[3349,3424,"Mr. Franco,"],[3478,3699,"it is an honor to finally hear from you."],[3699,3807,"I, I tell you what,"],[3807,3945,"I have been looking forward to this."],[3945,4083,"And it's so kind of you to,"],[4120,4254,"to bring the proposal with you..."],[4254,4320,"I..."],[4387,4475,"And you are?"]],"40":[[45,120,"And you are?"],[400,462,"I-"],[525,750,"Sir, we have definitely met before."],[750,829,"You don't remember me?"],[829,1009,"I'm Preston Norton."],[1009,1217,"I'm heir to the Norton family